author: palmtree5
install_msg: [p]help Hpapi to see commands. Don't forget to set your key with [p]hpset apikey <your_key>. If you need a key, log onto mc.hypixel.net and do /api. NOTE: API changes may break portions of this cog without warning.
end_user_data_statement: This extension does not store end user data.
name: Hpapi
short: Cog for getting info from the Hypixel API
description: Gets data from the Hypixel API including player stats, guild info, and active boosters
